'''杏'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Prunus armeniaca}}''），其果又稱'''杏子'''、'''杏實'''、'''杏桃'''，是[[李属|李属]][[李亚属|李亚属]][[植物|植物]]，其果肉、[[杏仁|果仁]]均可食用。

== 起源 ==
歐洲的杏是從[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]引進的<ref name=DP>{{cite book | first=M. le Baron | last=De Poerderlé | title=Manuel de l'Arboriste et du Forestier Belgiques: Seconde Édition: Tome Premier | publisher=Emmanuel Flon | location = à Bruxelles |year = 1788 | page = 682 }}</ref>，因此杏的學名种加词是亚美尼亚。但群体遗传学研究表明杏起源于[[中亚|中亚]]，在中亚和[[中国|中国]]发生至少三次独立的[[驯化|驯化]]事件，而后传入其它地区。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The complex evolutionary history of apricots: Species divergence, gene flow and multiple domestication events|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/mec.15296|last=Liu|first=Shuo|last2=Cornille|first2=Amandine|date=2019|journal=Molecular Ecology|issue=24|doi=10.1111/mec.15296|volume=28|pages=5299–5314|language=en|issn=1365-294X|last3=Decroocq|first3=Stéphane|last4=Tricon|first4=David|last5=Chague|first5=Aurélie|last6=Eyquard|first6=Jean-Philippe|last7=Liu|first7=Wei-Sheng|last8=Giraud|first8=Tatiana|last9=Decroocq|first9=Véronique|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623104145/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/mec.15296|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Genetic structure of a worldwide germplasm collection of ''Prunus armeniaca'' L. reveals three major diffusion routes for varieties coming from the species' center of origin|url=https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fpls.2020.00638/full|last=Bourguiba|first=Hedia|last2=Scotti|first2=Ivan|date=2020|journal=Frontiers in Plant Science|doi=10.3389/fpls.2020.00638|volume=11|language=en|issn=1664-462X|pmc=PMC7261834|pmid=32523597|last3=Sauvage|first3=Christopher|last4=Zhebentyayeva|first4=Tetyana|last5=Ledbetter|first5=Craig|last6=Krška|first6=Boris|last7=Remay|first7=Arnaud|last8=D’Onofrio|first8=Claudio|last9=Iketani|first9=Hiroyuki|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308051354/https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fpls.2020.00638/full|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 形态特征 ==

[[File:Apricot_tree_flowers.jpg|thumb]]的杏花]]

[[File:Apricot_and_cross_section.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Apricot_Trees_Japan.jpg|thumb]]
落叶[[乔木|乔木]]，高{{convert|8|–|12|m}}，樹幹直徑約{{convert|40|cm}}。阔卵形或圆卵形叶子，边缘有钝锯齿，長{{convert|5|–|9|cm}}，寬{{convert|4|–|8|cm}}。近叶柄顶端有二腺体；淡红色花单生或2－3个同生；圆、长圆或扁圆形[[核果|核果]]，果皮多为金黄色，向阳部有红晕和斑点；暗黄色果肉，味甜多汁；核面平滑没有斑孔，核缘厚而有沟纹。<ref name="foc">{{Cite web |title=Armeniaca vulgaris in Flora of China @ efloras.org |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200010636 |url-status=live |website=www.efloras.org |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224172056/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200010636 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |access-date=2022-06-25}}</ref><ref name=rushforth>Rushforth, K. (1999). ''Trees of Britain and Europe''. Collins {{ISBN|0-00-220013-9}}.</ref>

== 栽培与使用 ==
{{參見|杏仁}}
[[中医|中医]]认为杏有润肺定喘、生津止渴之用。民谚云：“端午吃个杏，到老没有病”。但又忌諱多吃，有“桃養人、杏傷人、李子樹下埋死人”之說。《[[日华子本草|日华子本草]]》認為杏“热，有毒”。《[[本草衍义|本草衍义]]》也說：“小儿尤不可食，多食致疮痈及上膈热”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.zhzyw.com/sg/dq/141213107GD1CG3DD4JI45AD.html|title=杏|publisher=中醫中藥網|access-date=2018-09-29|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507113108/https://www.zhzyw.com/sg/dq/141213107GD1CG3DD4JI45AD.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 文化 ==
相传[[三国|三国]]时[[孙吴|东吴]]有位名医叫[[董奉|董奉]]，精通医道，有妙手回春之术，医德也高。他晚年为百姓治病不收诊费和药钱，但要求病人痊愈后必须到山上种植[[杏树|杏树]]，名为“康乐杏”。后来，'''杏林'''用来专指医术精良，医德高尚的医生。<ref>{{cite book | author = [[葛洪|葛洪]] | title = [[神仙传|神仙传]] |year = | location = [[东晋|东晋]] |volume = 第十卷 }}</ref>

